{"commentv2": 1, "number": 5, "id": 2516254, "nreplies": 7, "sticky": 0, "user": "vindurza", "body": "after reveals from argus it turns out she is evil to a certain extent because, she tried to force her power upon illadin despite him telling her no and had Alleria locked up and tortured for investigating the void! that is not not what a character aligned with good intentions does.", "date": "2017-08-29T22:20:26-05:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Many dubious acts were done by heroes and characters for the sake of greater good. Attack of death knights for the body of Tirion, for example.", "creationdate": "2017-08-30T10:43:38-05:00", "id": 1069245, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2516254, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Helgos", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Still, she sounded genuinely creepy. I think it's safe to assume that Blizzard is revealing the Light as not the force of true \"good\" that everyone though it was. Which is amazing imo. Both Void and Light just want to destroy each other and everyone else are just pawns.", "creationdate": "2017-09-01T16:06:42-05:00", "id": 1070191, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2516254, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "evodas", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Agree, paint her green and she's like any Legion master. That thing about forcing Illidan to embrace the light's power and the comment that Alleria makes when entering the Xenedar about being throw in a cell for going against her whishers are not good signs.", "creationdate": "2017-09-04T21:38:22-05:00", "id": 1071545, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2516254, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "LegionNoob", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "\"Somestimes the hand of fate must be forced.\" - Illidan Stormrage", "creationdate": "2017-09-11T10:20:21-05:00", "id": 1073632, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2516254, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Keydiam", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Interesting side note, when you use Demon Hunter's \"Spectral Sight\" on her, she glows red right before the cut scene where you resurrect her and she tries to turn Illidan \"Holy\"", "creationdate": "2020-09-10T19:40:07-05:00", "id": 1389146, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2516254, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "dragontooth", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2017-08-29T22:21:13-05:00", 1, "vindurza"]}
